WEBVTT

00:08.000 --> 00:10.416
(slow footsteps approaching)

00:25.583 --> 00:27.750
You mourn the loss

00:25.583 --> 00:27.750
of your power?

00:27.750 --> 00:31.916
I once sensed every element

00:27.750 --> 00:31.916
that binds this world,

00:31.916 --> 00:35.916
felt them as one breathes air.

00:35.916 --> 00:38.875
But I gave unto you

00:35.916 --> 00:38.875
that which you deserve.

00:38.875 --> 00:41.833
My strength grows each day.

00:41.833 --> 00:44.833
Perhaps a small token

00:41.833 --> 00:44.833
of my affection...

00:44.833 --> 00:46.875
is warranted.

00:57.875 --> 01:00.000
(grunts)

01:01.500 --> 01:03.083
My love,

01:03.083 --> 01:06.041
I received but only

01:03.083 --> 01:06.041
a fraction of my power.

01:06.041 --> 01:09.208
Now you know

01:06.041 --> 01:09.208
exactly how I feel.

01:09.208 --> 01:13.666
Summoning one pitiful creature

01:09.208 --> 01:13.666
at a time to feed my hunger.

01:13.666 --> 01:18.375
Existing on drops of rain

01:13.666 --> 01:18.375
rather than a flood.

01:23.166 --> 01:25.250
You wish to be my equal?

01:26.958 --> 01:29.083
Then as I suffer...

01:29.083 --> 01:32.375
so shall you.

01:36.958 --> 01:40.583
(panting)

01:40.583 --> 01:43.208
Hands where

01:40.583 --> 01:43.208
I can see 'em!

01:40.583 --> 01:43.208
(coughing)

01:45.333 --> 01:47.375
Atticus Nevins.

01:47.375 --> 01:49.791
FBI's most wanted.

01:49.791 --> 01:52.041
Looks like your

01:49.791 --> 01:52.041
running days are over.

01:52.041 --> 01:54.250
(police radio chirps)

01:52.041 --> 01:54.250
This is Hammond. I got him.

01:54.250 --> 01:55.875
Meet me back at the road.

01:55.875 --> 01:57.291
Tell dispatch

01:55.875 --> 01:57.291
we'll need transpo and escort.

01:57.291 --> 01:58.500
Copy that, calling it in.

01:58.500 --> 01:59.833
How did you find me?

01:59.833 --> 02:01.250
Security footage caught you

02:01.250 --> 02:02.958
near a storage facility

02:01.250 --> 02:02.958
in Elmsford.

02:02.958 --> 02:04.541
Don't feel bad.

02:04.541 --> 02:06.458
Everyone's luck runs out

02:04.541 --> 02:06.458
sooner or later.

02:06.458 --> 02:09.000
(growling)

02:09.000 --> 02:10.500
What was that?

02:10.500 --> 02:12.916
Stay put.

02:18.375 --> 02:20.041
(growling)

02:20.041 --> 02:22.416
(yelling):

02:20.041 --> 02:22.416
No! No!

02:22.416 --> 02:28.458
(singing along with recording):

02:22.416 --> 02:28.458
♪ O sole mio... ♪

02:29.500 --> 02:31.750
(singing in Italian)

02:33.666 --> 02:35.458
(Italian opera song continues)

02:41.083 --> 02:44.083
(resumes singing)

02:50.666 --> 02:52.208
(humming)

02:55.166 --> 02:56.875
(song ends)

02:56.875 --> 02:58.833
Salud.

02:58.833 --> 03:02.041
(door opening)

03:02.041 --> 03:06.041
Buona sera, Signorina.

03:06.041 --> 03:07.375
Buona sera.

03:07.375 --> 03:10.750
Okay.

03:10.750 --> 03:13.458
You know I'm loving the

03:10.750 --> 03:13.458
five-star treatment, but...

03:13.458 --> 03:15.666
you got to stop

03:13.458 --> 03:15.666
spoiling me, Crane.

03:15.666 --> 03:17.041
(laughs)

03:17.041 --> 03:19.416
When patriot prisoners of war

03:19.416 --> 03:22.333
were freed after the British

03:19.416 --> 03:22.333
retreated from Philadelphia,

03:22.333 --> 03:27.875
they dined for weeks in order

03:22.333 --> 03:27.875
to revive their broken spirits.

03:27.875 --> 03:30.958
You know, I fended for myself

03:27.875 --> 03:30.958
ten months

03:30.958 --> 03:32.541
in those catacombs.

03:32.541 --> 03:34.916
I don't need

03:32.541 --> 03:34.916
to be pampered, Crane.

03:34.916 --> 03:39.291
You, Lieutenant,

03:34.916 --> 03:39.291
are a woman of infinite pride

03:39.291 --> 03:41.666
and unparalleled

03:39.291 --> 03:41.666
resourcefulness.

03:41.666 --> 03:43.083
But...

03:44.750 --> 03:47.250
...after the deprivation

03:44.750 --> 03:47.250
you endured...

03:48.625 --> 03:51.833
...this is the very least

03:48.625 --> 03:51.833
I could do.

03:57.166 --> 03:58.833
Mm, and a reminder.

03:58.833 --> 04:00.958
We are to attend

04:00.958 --> 04:04.125
the cinema this evening

04:00.958 --> 04:04.125
with Miss Jenny and Master Joe.

04:04.125 --> 04:06.958
Top of the billing

04:04.125 --> 04:06.958
at the Music Hall is  E.T.,

04:06.958 --> 04:09.958
which apparently concerns

04:06.958 --> 04:09.958
a diminutive being

04:09.958 --> 04:12.583
stranded far from home.

04:15.250 --> 04:18.208
Perhaps

04:15.250 --> 04:18.208
a different suggestion...

04:18.208 --> 04:21.458
No. Crane,  E.T.'s  a classic.

04:18.208 --> 04:21.458
You should see it.

04:21.458 --> 04:23.875
Truth is I came home

04:21.458 --> 04:23.875
to pick up a few things.

04:23.875 --> 04:25.541
I booked some time at the range.

04:25.541 --> 04:28.791
Gotten a little rusty

04:25.541 --> 04:28.791
since I've been away, so,

04:28.791 --> 04:31.083
keep it warm for me.

04:31.083 --> 04:33.250
Yes, of course I can.

04:34.833 --> 04:36.291
Are you maintaining a journal?

04:36.291 --> 04:38.291
Yeah, it's supposed to help me

04:38.291 --> 04:40.083
"define and sort

04:38.291 --> 04:40.083
through my trauma,"

04:40.083 --> 04:41.666
but seeing

04:40.083 --> 04:41.666
as how every day

04:41.666 --> 04:44.291
I was down there was the same

04:41.666 --> 04:44.291
as the one before,

04:44.291 --> 04:45.708
it makes for

04:44.291 --> 04:45.708
a pretty boring read.

04:45.708 --> 04:47.250
And...

04:47.250 --> 04:49.458
to answer the question

04:47.250 --> 04:49.458
that you are thinking,

04:49.458 --> 04:52.625
but not asking directly...

04:52.625 --> 04:54.041
I'm fine.

04:55.333 --> 04:56.750
And thanks to you,

04:56.750 --> 05:01.666
I'm taking it all

04:56.750 --> 05:01.666
meal by splendid meal.

05:01.666 --> 05:04.000
Signore Crane.

05:04.000 --> 05:05.583
Tenente.

05:10.666 --> 05:12.166
(door closes)

05:22.333 --> 05:25.208
Sure you don't want me

05:22.333 --> 05:25.208
to come in with you?

05:26.458 --> 05:28.333
I'm sure.

05:28.333 --> 05:29.875
You can do this, Jen.

05:29.875 --> 05:32.375
You need to.

05:39.000 --> 05:41.375
(indistinct chatter)

05:46.875 --> 05:48.083
Hey.

05:48.083 --> 05:49.875
Thanks for meeting me.

05:49.875 --> 05:53.125
Hope I didn't bring you

05:49.875 --> 05:53.125
too far out of your way.

05:56.375 --> 05:58.541
I was surprised

05:56.375 --> 05:58.541
you took my call.

05:58.541 --> 06:00.875
You kind of caught me off guard.

06:04.125 --> 06:06.250
You're the spitting image

06:04.125 --> 06:06.250
of your mother, you know?

06:06.250 --> 06:07.958
Same hair,

06:07.958 --> 06:10.208
eyes.

06:07.958 --> 06:10.208
This is a mistake.

06:10.208 --> 06:12.666
Jennifer, Jennifer, wait.

06:15.541 --> 06:18.541
Look, you don't owe me anything,

06:18.541 --> 06:20.250
but for what it's worth,

06:20.250 --> 06:22.750
I'm just here to listen

06:20.250 --> 06:22.750
to whatever you need to say.

06:25.458 --> 06:28.125
I have hated you

06:25.458 --> 06:28.125
for as long as I can remember.

06:28.125 --> 06:31.333
I've had epic conversations

06:28.125 --> 06:31.333
with you in my mind,

06:31.333 --> 06:33.208
just telling you all

06:33.208 --> 06:34.916
the many, many reasons

06:34.916 --> 06:36.208
I think

06:34.916 --> 06:36.208
you're a terrible person.

06:38.541 --> 06:41.291
Asking you why you abandoned us,

06:41.291 --> 06:44.125
how you could just walk away

06:41.291 --> 06:44.125
from your family.

06:45.375 --> 06:47.125
(scoffs)

06:47.125 --> 06:48.833
But now that you're sitting here

06:47.125 --> 06:48.833
right in front of me,

06:48.833 --> 06:51.291
I don't know

06:48.833 --> 06:51.291
what to say to you.

06:56.166 --> 06:58.125
I'd say you're closing in on it.

06:58.125 --> 07:00.041
Why did you leave us?

07:01.583 --> 07:02.750
Because of Mom?

07:02.750 --> 07:03.916
No.

07:03.916 --> 07:05.916
No, it was me.

07:07.125 --> 07:10.458
When her illness

07:07.125 --> 07:10.458
kicked in...

07:10.458 --> 07:13.208
I didn't know

07:10.458 --> 07:13.208
how to handle it.

07:13.208 --> 07:15.000
And being a fool, I drank.

07:15.000 --> 07:16.750
In the end,

07:15.000 --> 07:16.750
I joined the Navy

07:16.750 --> 07:18.583
because we needed

07:16.750 --> 07:18.583
medical benefits.

07:18.583 --> 07:20.500
I also needed to sober up.

07:20.500 --> 07:23.666
So, they shipped me overseas,

07:20.500 --> 07:23.666
long-term deployments.

07:23.666 --> 07:26.791
I stayed

07:23.666 --> 07:26.791
for three consecutive tours.

07:26.791 --> 07:29.083
And when I got out

07:26.791 --> 07:29.083
six years later,

07:29.083 --> 07:31.041
life had moved on.

07:31.041 --> 07:33.000
Yeah, Mom was dead.

07:33.000 --> 07:35.166
Abbie and me were

07:33.000 --> 07:35.166
in foster care.

07:35.166 --> 07:38.458
And I've lived with the shame

07:35.166 --> 07:38.458
and regret for decades.

07:40.916 --> 07:42.916
But I'm not here

07:42.916 --> 07:45.166
looking for absolution

07:45.166 --> 07:46.208
or forgiveness.

07:46.208 --> 07:47.541
Then what do you want?

07:47.541 --> 07:49.375
To tell you...

07:49.375 --> 07:51.041
there wasn't anything you did,

07:51.041 --> 07:54.916
or your sister,

07:51.041 --> 07:54.916
or your mother.

07:54.916 --> 07:57.291
I think it's important

07:54.916 --> 07:57.291
you both hear that from me.

07:58.625 --> 08:00.916
I'd like to see Abbie.

08:07.083 --> 08:10.041
(gunshots)

08:21.208 --> 08:22.458
(gunshots)

08:27.833 --> 08:30.125
(gunshots)

08:41.625 --> 08:43.083
(sighs)

08:43.083 --> 08:44.708
Maybe lay off

08:43.083 --> 08:44.708
the coffee.

08:44.708 --> 08:46.541
Might be giving you

08:44.708 --> 08:46.541
the jitters.

08:48.166 --> 08:49.666
I don't drink the stuff anymore.

08:49.666 --> 08:51.166
Maybe start up again.

08:51.166 --> 08:52.625
I'm gonna chalk this up

08:52.625 --> 08:55.500
to us both having

08:52.625 --> 08:55.500
A type personalities.

08:55.500 --> 08:57.125
Seemed like a better option

08:57.125 --> 08:59.958
than take-out food

08:57.125 --> 08:59.958
and paperwork. You?

08:59.958 --> 09:03.000
I needed to clear my head,

08:59.958 --> 09:03.000
that's all.

09:03.000 --> 09:04.666
Maybe I should

09:03.000 --> 09:04.666
have checked to see

09:04.666 --> 09:07.291
if you had time booked

09:04.666 --> 09:07.291
before I showed up.

09:07.291 --> 09:09.333
It's fine, Danny.

09:11.250 --> 09:14.291
So our talk

09:11.250 --> 09:14.291
the other day...

09:14.291 --> 09:17.500
I said some things I

09:14.291 --> 09:17.500
wasn't expecting to admit.

09:21.083 --> 09:23.125
You said 'em.

09:23.125 --> 09:25.750
And, honestly,

09:23.125 --> 09:25.750
I meant them.

09:25.750 --> 09:27.166
Not to make

09:25.750 --> 09:27.166
things awkward,

09:27.166 --> 09:29.291
but to get things

09:27.166 --> 09:29.291
back on track for us.

09:29.291 --> 09:31.083
You know, having each

09:29.291 --> 09:31.083
other's backs again,

09:31.083 --> 09:33.125
trusting each other.

09:33.125 --> 09:35.500
Things happened, the Nevins

09:33.125 --> 09:35.500
case, but that doesn't mean

09:35.500 --> 09:38.125
we have to throw away everything

09:35.500 --> 09:38.125
we worked so hard to build.

09:40.041 --> 09:41.666
It's too important.

09:41.666 --> 09:44.125
You're  too important.

09:46.750 --> 09:49.333
Maybe next time

09:46.750 --> 09:49.333
we have a chat like this,

09:49.333 --> 09:52.833
it's not in the FBI gun range

09:49.333 --> 09:52.833
at 8:00 at night.

09:52.833 --> 09:55.250
There's a pancake house

09:52.833 --> 09:55.250
around the corner,

09:55.250 --> 09:57.000
if you want to be

09:55.250 --> 09:57.000
a diva about it.

09:57.000 --> 09:58.583
Another time.

09:57.000 --> 09:58.583
Woman with a gun.

09:58.583 --> 10:00.041
(laughs)

10:00.041 --> 10:02.041
I heard that.

10:02.041 --> 10:03.666
(phone buzzes)

10:03.666 --> 10:07.000
(sighs)

10:13.291 --> 10:15.166
(phone buzzes)

10:21.500 --> 10:22.750
(coughing) Please don't shoot.

10:22.750 --> 10:24.000
Nevins?!

10:24.000 --> 10:25.458
Mills, thank God

10:24.000 --> 10:25.458
you got my message.

10:25.458 --> 10:27.166
Hands behind your head!

10:27.166 --> 10:28.375
The a reason I...

10:27.166 --> 10:28.375
Now!

10:28.375 --> 10:30.375
(coughing)

10:28.375 --> 10:30.375
Up against the tree.

10:30.375 --> 10:31.791
I don't know

10:30.375 --> 10:31.791
if you're stupid or crazy,

10:31.791 --> 10:34.250
but I'm bringing you in.

10:34.250 --> 10:35.416
(handcuffs jangling)

10:35.416 --> 10:37.000
Hand.

10:38.166 --> 10:40.666
(grunts)

10:38.166 --> 10:40.666
(coughing)

10:42.916 --> 10:44.916
What in the hell happened

10:42.916 --> 10:44.916
to you?

10:44.916 --> 10:46.291
Another run-in with Pandora?

10:46.291 --> 10:47.750
Worse.

10:53.500 --> 10:54.708
You saw what did this?

10:54.708 --> 10:56.166
It came after me, too.

10:56.166 --> 10:57.250
It's inhuman.

10:57.250 --> 10:58.458
It's unstoppable.

10:58.458 --> 11:00.625
I know this creature, Mills.

11:00.625 --> 11:03.791
If you want to stop it,

11:00.625 --> 11:03.791
you need my help.

11:06.833 --> 11:09.833
♪ ♪

11:46.208 --> 11:48.208
This is cozy.

11:48.208 --> 11:50.291
It's a monster-proof cell.

11:50.291 --> 11:52.250
Should be plenty

11:50.291 --> 11:52.250
to hold a worm like you.

11:54.166 --> 11:55.791
I don't know what attacked you,

11:55.791 --> 11:57.958
but it's too bad

11:55.791 --> 11:57.958
it didn't finish the job.

11:57.958 --> 11:59.291
We didn't end things

11:59.291 --> 12:01.041
on good terms, did we?

11:59.291 --> 12:01.041
Oh, what,

12:01.041 --> 12:02.541
you mean when you

12:01.041 --> 12:02.541
almost put a bullet in my head?

12:02.541 --> 12:04.416
JENNY: Or when you helped

12:02.541 --> 12:04.416
Pandora raise an evil god

12:04.416 --> 12:05.833
that almost killed us all?

12:05.833 --> 12:07.375
Yeah, I guess

12:05.833 --> 12:07.375
we're not quite over it.

12:07.375 --> 12:09.416
Hey, I'm the one

12:07.375 --> 12:09.416
who was shot, who was arrested,

12:09.416 --> 12:11.583
who lived on the streets

12:09.416 --> 12:11.583
like an animal.

12:11.583 --> 12:13.583
Whatever you went through,

12:11.583 --> 12:13.583
I don't think it was enough.

12:13.583 --> 12:15.291
Are you sure

12:13.583 --> 12:15.291
about that, son?

12:16.458 --> 12:18.000
Take a look.

12:23.500 --> 12:25.958
My God.

12:25.958 --> 12:27.458
It's pretty, isn't it?

12:27.458 --> 12:28.750
(coughing)

12:28.750 --> 12:29.916
Pandora wanted

12:28.750 --> 12:29.916
her pound of flesh,

12:29.916 --> 12:31.500
but she wanted it literally.

12:32.666 --> 12:33.750
(grunting)

12:33.750 --> 12:35.208
Did you know a man

12:35.208 --> 12:36.708
can live without a spleen?

12:38.750 --> 12:41.083
Pandora promised

12:38.750 --> 12:41.083
him riches and glory

12:41.083 --> 12:44.083
in exchange for obtaining

12:41.083 --> 12:44.083
the Eye of Providence for her.

12:44.083 --> 12:47.666
When he failed to do so,

12:44.083 --> 12:47.666
she terminated his services.

12:47.666 --> 12:50.583
How the mighty fall.

12:50.583 --> 12:51.833
JOE: All right,

12:50.583 --> 12:51.833
so why'd you come to us, huh?

12:51.833 --> 12:53.666
Big fish like you,

12:53.666 --> 12:55.500
I mean, you must have a lot of

12:53.666 --> 12:55.500
people you can go to for help.

12:55.500 --> 12:57.500
Oh, yeah. One little arrest,

12:57.500 --> 12:59.750
all my associates

12:57.500 --> 12:59.750
turn their backs on me,

12:59.750 --> 13:01.875
huh?

12:59.750 --> 13:01.875
So I see your angle.

13:01.875 --> 13:04.000
You help us catch

13:01.875 --> 13:04.000
the monster...

13:04.000 --> 13:05.458
And we help you get out of town.

13:05.458 --> 13:06.875
I need some assurances.

13:06.875 --> 13:08.875
Safe passage out of the country.

13:08.875 --> 13:12.041
Passport,

13:08.875 --> 13:12.041
money that can't be traced.

13:08.875 --> 13:12.041
Thanks but...

13:12.041 --> 13:14.666
we'll find the creature

13:12.041 --> 13:14.666
ourselves.

13:14.666 --> 13:17.208
No, you won't.

13:17.208 --> 13:19.333
Not without my help.

13:19.333 --> 13:22.250
This isn't one

13:19.333 --> 13:22.250
of Pandora's utility players.

13:22.250 --> 13:24.458
You won't believe

13:22.250 --> 13:24.458
where it comes from.

13:25.500 --> 13:26.750
People are dying out there.

13:26.750 --> 13:28.166
We need him to talk.

13:28.166 --> 13:29.583
This calls to mind

13:28.166 --> 13:29.583
an interrogation tactic

13:29.583 --> 13:30.583
of Washington's.

13:30.583 --> 13:33.625
Now, if used properly,

13:33.625 --> 13:36.500
it could encourage him

13:33.625 --> 13:36.500
to loosen his tongue.

13:38.041 --> 13:40.458
(coughing)

13:38.041 --> 13:40.458
(door opens)

13:42.708 --> 13:44.916
Here's the deal:

13:42.708 --> 13:44.916
depending on the value

13:44.916 --> 13:47.125
of the information

13:44.916 --> 13:47.125
that you give us,

13:47.125 --> 13:50.458
we will consider getting you

13:47.125 --> 13:50.458
across the Canadian border.

13:50.458 --> 13:54.083
No guarantees, no assurances.

13:54.083 --> 13:56.083
And as a gesture of good faith,

13:56.083 --> 13:57.791
in accordance with

13:56.083 --> 13:57.791
the proper treatment

13:57.791 --> 14:01.625
of prisoners and with the

13:57.791 --> 14:01.625
proviso you cooperate,

14:01.625 --> 14:03.250
you shall be fed.

14:05.791 --> 14:07.416
ABBIE:

14:05.791 --> 14:07.416
But if you mess with us,

14:07.416 --> 14:09.375
we will gift wrap you

14:07.416 --> 14:09.375
to the FBI.

14:14.916 --> 14:17.375
(chewing,

14:14.916 --> 14:17.375
crunching sounds)

14:22.958 --> 14:24.583
Ugh.

14:24.583 --> 14:26.041
Uh...

14:29.625 --> 14:30.666
ABBIE:

14:29.625 --> 14:30.666
You said that you had

14:30.666 --> 14:32.958
information about this creature.

14:36.291 --> 14:38.125
'91. Iraq.

14:38.125 --> 14:40.375
End of Gulf War One.

14:40.375 --> 14:42.291
Pulling back

14:40.375 --> 14:42.291
from Al Busayyah,

14:42.291 --> 14:44.291
rumor starts to float around

14:42.291 --> 14:44.291
about a cave,

14:44.291 --> 14:46.125
just north of the Saudi border.

