16:44.125 --> 16:47.041
It was his first contact

16:44.125 --> 16:47.041
with the supernatural,

16:47.041 --> 16:48.791
and it never left him.

16:48.791 --> 16:51.208
Imagine my shock

16:48.791 --> 16:51.208
when the same damn creature

16:51.208 --> 16:53.625
shows up in Sleepy Hollow.

16:53.625 --> 16:55.875
That's a good story. This

16:53.625 --> 16:55.875
helps us find the creature how?

16:55.875 --> 16:59.291
You take me

16:55.875 --> 16:59.291
to August's files.

16:59.291 --> 17:03.041
I guarantee

16:59.291 --> 17:03.041
you'll get what you need.

17:03.041 --> 17:05.833
You mean these files?

17:03.041 --> 17:05.833
JOE: Yeah, we've gone

17:03.041 --> 17:05.833
