17:05.833 --> 17:07.833
There's nothing that matches

17:05.833 --> 17:07.833
the creature you described.

17:09.416 --> 17:10.375
Mother, may I?

17:11.625 --> 17:14.041
Yeah.

17:14.041 --> 17:15.208
(clicking)

17:18.750 --> 17:20.375
(sighs)

17:25.833 --> 17:27.833
Now, what you all

17:25.833 --> 17:27.833
don't know is

17:27.833 --> 17:32.416
what a paranoid bastard

17:27.833 --> 17:32.416
ol' Sheriff Corbin was.

17:35.958 --> 17:37.833
He had major...

17:39.250 --> 17:41.666
(thump, click)

17:43.083 --> 17:45.375
...trust issues.

17:48.166 --> 17:52.458
You want to know everything he

17:48.166 --> 17:52.458
knew about that-that-that thing?

17:52.458 --> 17:54.000
Try August Corbin's

17:54.000 --> 17:56.666
case file number one.

17:56.666 --> 17:59.208
All right. Come on.

18:02.666 --> 18:04.833
Well, according

18:02.666 --> 18:04.833
to the sheriff's research,

18:04.833 --> 18:08.000
the creature is an ancient

18:04.833 --> 18:08.000
Mesopotamian  ghallu,

18:08.000 --> 18:10.541
more commonly known

18:08.000 --> 18:10.541
as a demonic ghoul.

18:10.541 --> 18:12.708
They're used as guardians

18:10.541 --> 18:12.708
of sacred temples and crypts.

18:12.708 --> 18:15.083
Ruthless predators,

18:12.708 --> 18:15.083
said to hunt without mercy.

18:15.083 --> 18:16.583
Ah, here.

18:15.083 --> 18:16.583
The creature's

18:16.583 --> 18:18.541
only weakness is something known

18:18.541 --> 18:21.083
as an  Aurum Scarabaeus Sacer.

18:23.333 --> 18:24.625
A Golden Scarab.

18:24.625 --> 18:26.250
"Whomsoever possesses the scarab

18:26.250 --> 18:28.833
"shall become master

18:26.250 --> 18:28.833
to the ghoul, which will perform

18:28.833 --> 18:30.166
