This is Nevins

18:41.375 --> 18:43.000
we're talking about.

18:43.000 --> 18:44.916
Mr. Loyalty Is Dead.

18:44.916 --> 18:47.541
Hey. Randall Martin's stock

18:44.916 --> 18:47.541
is rising.

18:47.541 --> 18:49.666
If he's gonna take over

18:47.541 --> 18:49.666
Nevins' operation,

18:49.666 --> 18:52.708
we have got to get

18:49.666 --> 18:52.708
into his good books.

