The place has

19:02.875 --> 19:05.541
been cleaned out.

19:05.541 --> 19:08.208
By who? Randall?

19:08.208 --> 19:10.458
(sighs)

19:08.208 --> 19:10.458
Someone got here first.

19:10.458 --> 19:13.083
Vin...

19:14.291 --> 19:15.416
(screaming)

19:21.500 --> 19:23.583
No one knows anything

19:21.500 --> 19:23.583
about a golden artifact

19:21.500 --> 19:23.583
that controls a ghoul.

19:25.000 --> 19:26.625
Hey, is this a bad time?

19:25.000 --> 19:26.625
Reynolds is running

19:26.625 --> 19:28.125
a briefing in a few minutes,

19:28.125 --> 19:29.333
and I can't find

19:28.125 --> 19:29.333
the damn statewide warrant list.

19:29.333 --> 19:30.500
I saw Dad.

19:30.500 --> 19:33.375
Yesterday.

19:33.375 --> 19:36.458
I wasn't completely sure

19:33.375 --> 19:36.458
I wanted to tell you.

19:36.458 --> 19:38.291
It's not exactly the right time.

19:38.291 --> 19:41.291
It's never really

19:38.291 --> 19:41.291
the right time.

19:38.291 --> 19:41.291
Abbie,

19:41.291 --> 19:44.291
you're different

19:41.291 --> 19:44.291
than before you disappeared.

19:44.291 --> 19:46.125
You're dealing

19:44.291 --> 19:46.125
with it every day.

19:46.125 --> 19:47.541
Don't think

19:46.125 --> 19:47.541
I can't see that.

19:47.541 --> 19:50.291
I know when

19:47.541 --> 19:50.291
you're hurting.

19:50.291 --> 19:52.916
I don't want anything

19:50.291 --> 19:52.916
to cause you more pain.

19:55.208 --> 19:57.416
That's not your call, sis.

19:57.416 --> 19:59.250
I know.

19:59.250 --> 20:02.250
Which is why I'm here right now.

20:02.250 --> 20:04.791
He wants to see you.

20:04.791 --> 20:07.041
What'd you tell him?

20:07.041 --> 20:08.708
Told him I'd talk to you.

20:08.708 --> 20:09.750
You did.

20:09.750 --> 20:11.041
I appreciate it.

20:16.791 --> 20:18.291
(sighs)

20:18.291 --> 20:21.125
What did it feel like,

20:21.125 --> 20:22.958
seeing him?

20:22.958 --> 20:24.708
It wasn't easy.

20:32.166 --> 20:34.166
Gary Wallis and Vincent Rota.

20:34.166 --> 20:36.791
Found in a storage unit

20:34.166 --> 20:36.791
in Elmsford.

20:36.791 --> 20:40.208
Similar M.O. to the first

20:36.791 --> 20:40.208
killing in Pocantico Hills.

20:40.208 --> 20:42.666
Evidence of rage. Overkill.

20:42.666 --> 20:44.250
Ritualistic evisceration.

20:44.250 --> 20:46.875
Wallis and Rota

20:44.250 --> 20:46.875
were known associates

20:46.875 --> 20:48.916
of Atticus Nevins,

20:46.875 --> 20:48.916
who's still at large.

20:48.916 --> 20:50.416
The storage unit

20:50.416 --> 20:53.250
was rented by a shell company

20:50.416 --> 20:53.250
controlled by Nevins.

20:53.250 --> 20:55.625
Which means

20:53.250 --> 20:55.625
this could be

20:55.625 --> 20:58.208
a rival moving in

20:55.625 --> 20:58.208
on his old operation.

20:58.208 --> 21:00.041
We're working

20:58.208 --> 21:00.041
to figure out

21:00.041 --> 21:01.708
what kind of murder

21:00.041 --> 21:01.708
weapon was resonsible

21:01.708 --> 21:03.083
for these wounds.

21:03.083 --> 21:04.958
Forensics is sorting...

21:03.083 --> 21:04.958
(voice fades)

21:04.958 --> 21:08.375
(indistinct whispering)

21:04.958 --> 21:08.375
Beautiful.

21:12.458 --> 21:14.708
SOPHIE (quietly):

21:12.458 --> 21:14.708
Hey.

21:14.708 --> 21:16.791
Hey.

21:16.791 --> 21:19.166
You okay?

21:21.041 --> 21:22.791
Migraine coming on.

21:22.791 --> 21:24.666
Oh.

21:24.666 --> 21:26.500
A kill this violent

21:24.666 --> 21:26.500
is a big statement.

21:26.500 --> 21:30.750
Is it just me or is all of this

21:26.500 --> 21:30.750
way too close to Nevins?

21:30.750 --> 21:32.125
Creature goes after Nevins,

21:32.125 --> 21:33.708
then takes out

21:32.125 --> 21:33.708
two of his own guys.

21:33.708 --> 21:35.625
There's definitely

21:33.708 --> 21:35.625
something we're missing.

21:35.625 --> 21:37.625
I'm gonna grab some old files.

21:37.625 --> 21:39.083
Buy me some time.

21:39.083 --> 21:41.083
Yeah, I got your back.

21:41.083 --> 21:43.875
♪ ♪

22:00.375 --> 22:02.958
Mmm. He's getting

22:00.375 --> 22:02.958
under your skin, isn't he?

