Two more men have died.

22:04.375 --> 22:06.125
If am to labor

22:04.375 --> 22:06.125
at finding answers,

22:06.125 --> 22:08.750
I refuse to be taunted

22:06.125 --> 22:08.750
by his blatant apathy.

22:08.750 --> 22:10.583
Still, despite

22:08.750 --> 22:10.583
my very best efforts,

22:10.583 --> 22:14.083
I'm no closer to finding

22:10.583 --> 22:14.083
scarab nor Ghoul.

22:14.083 --> 22:15.583
Yeah. I dug this up.

22:15.583 --> 22:18.541
Customs Enforcement list.

22:18.541 --> 22:20.083
Hundreds of missing

22:18.541 --> 22:20.083
ancient artifacts,

22:20.083 --> 22:22.041
including...

22:23.000 --> 22:26.000
The golden scarab.

22:26.000 --> 22:27.791
Mm-hmm. Main suspect

22:26.000 --> 22:27.791
in the case:

22:27.791 --> 22:30.125
Randall Martin.

22:30.125 --> 22:31.833
Former employee of Nevins,

22:31.833 --> 22:35.208
making a play to take over

22:31.833 --> 22:35.208
his whole operation.

22:35.208 --> 22:37.916
Whoever has the scarab

22:35.208 --> 22:37.916
controls the Ghoul.

22:37.916 --> 22:40.541
And if Mr. Martin wishes

22:37.916 --> 22:40.541
to be taken seriously

22:40.541 --> 22:42.583
as heir

22:40.541 --> 22:42.583
to Atticus Nevins' empire,

22:42.583 --> 22:46.250
having a vicious monster

22:42.583 --> 22:46.250
