Okay. I'm impressed.

23:21.708 --> 23:26.250
(panting)

23:26.250 --> 23:28.500
♪ ♪

23:30.791 --> 23:32.708
Looks ghoul-sized to me.

23:32.708 --> 23:34.958
(sighs) All right,

23:32.708 --> 23:34.958
