23:36.833 --> 23:38.916
Okay, careful.

23:36.833 --> 23:38.916
Yeah.

23:41.833 --> 23:43.625
(gun clicks)

23:45.666 --> 23:47.750
RANDALL: As much as I'd like

23:45.666 --> 23:47.750
to see your reaction,

23:47.750 --> 23:49.208
you don't want

23:47.750 --> 23:49.208
to open that crate.

