Guns on the ground,

23:50.458 --> 23:53.041
both of you

23:50.458 --> 23:53.041
on your knees.

23:53.041 --> 23:54.125
Right now!

23:54.125 --> 23:55.208
Okay.

23:55.208 --> 23:56.708
Yep.

