Look, Randall,

24:38.208 --> 24:40.958
we're all in danger, okay?

24:40.958 --> 24:43.416
The only ones in danger

24:40.958 --> 24:43.416
are you two.

24:43.416 --> 24:45.000
This is business.

24:45.000 --> 24:46.791
Nothing person...

