Hi.

26:06.458 --> 26:08.750
Abbie, Abbie,

26:06.458 --> 26:08.750
Randall is dead.

26:08.750 --> 26:10.083
He's not controlling the Ghoul.

26:10.083 --> 26:12.083
You need to search Nevins.

26:12.083 --> 26:13.416
We did. He's clean.

26:13.416 --> 26:15.375
No. No, Abbie, he's not clean.

26:15.375 --> 26:16.541
You need to search him again.

26:16.541 --> 26:18.250
Hang up the phone, Mills.

26:20.708 --> 26:21.791
You have the scarab.

