26:28.291 --> 26:31.791
See, when Pandora did

26:28.291 --> 26:31.791
that little splenectomy,

26:31.791 --> 26:33.333
she inadvertently

26:31.791 --> 26:33.333
gave me

26:33.333 --> 26:35.416
(crackling, squishing)

26:33.333 --> 26:35.416
a little...

26:35.416 --> 26:37.083
(groans):

26:35.416 --> 26:37.083
oh, just a little spot

26:37.083 --> 26:39.250
for some contraband.

26:42.750 --> 26:44.541
Come on.

26:45.750 --> 26:47.750
Come on.

26:47.750 --> 26:49.708
The cave in Iraq...

26:49.708 --> 26:52.458
you took more

26:49.708 --> 26:52.458
than just gold.

26:52.458 --> 26:54.041
Oh, even back then

26:54.041 --> 26:55.291
I was always

26:54.041 --> 26:55.291
looking for

26:55.291 --> 26:57.375
something extra-special to sell.

26:57.375 --> 27:00.458
I managed to sneak

26:57.375 --> 27:00.458
away from my unit

27:00.458 --> 27:03.041
and what do I find?

27:15.750 --> 27:17.041
(gasps)

27:17.041 --> 27:18.541
I had no idea

27:18.541 --> 27:21.791
the power I held

27:18.541 --> 27:21.791
in the palm of my hand.

27:21.791 --> 27:23.666
(growls)

27:25.875 --> 27:27.208
(panting)

27:29.791 --> 27:33.291
And then I felt it,

27:29.791 --> 27:33.291
immediately.

27:33.291 --> 27:35.666
I had complete control

27:33.291 --> 27:35.666
of the creature.

27:35.666 --> 27:37.750
(chuckles)

27:40.041 --> 27:42.875
One little thought

27:40.041 --> 27:42.875
entered my head.

27:42.875 --> 27:43.708
(screaming)

27:47.041 --> 27:49.625
Ambush! Fall back!

27:50.500 --> 27:52.625
(explosion)

27:56.791 --> 27:58.791
What the hell was that?

28:00.166 --> 28:02.125
(chitters)

28:05.750 --> 28:08.208
Pandora and her man may have

28:08.208 --> 28:09.416
summoned the creature,

28:09.416 --> 28:10.625
but I can control him.

28:10.625 --> 28:12.000
I just had to

28:12.000 --> 28:13.416
rescue this little sucker

28:13.416 --> 28:15.416
from one of my storage units.

28:17.625 --> 28:22.125
That cave turned out to be the

28:17.625 --> 28:22.125
tip of a very lucrative iceberg.

