Corbin identified dozens

28:23.916 --> 28:25.541
of crypts and tombs

28:23.916 --> 28:25.541
and every one of them

28:25.541 --> 28:27.458
had artifacts and creatures...

28:27.458 --> 28:29.250
Which you're gonna use

28:27.458 --> 28:29.250
to buy your freedom.

28:29.250 --> 28:30.500
I already have a buyer.

28:30.500 --> 28:33.500
I just... needed access.

28:33.500 --> 28:35.750
Bad plan,

28:33.500 --> 28:35.750
because you're going to jail.

28:35.750 --> 28:37.000
No, I'm not.

28:37.000 --> 28:38.250
Because...

28:38.250 --> 28:40.541
wait for it...

28:44.041 --> 28:45.541
(growling)

28:45.541 --> 28:46.541
(laughs)

28:50.666 --> 28:51.958
Fido, would

28:50.666 --> 28:51.958
you mind, uh...?

