one more trick to show you.

29:05.041 --> 29:07.125
(shrieking)

29:10.791 --> 29:13.041
It's been fun.

29:13.041 --> 29:14.708
Okay, Fido...

29:14.708 --> 29:16.083
sic 'em, boy.

29:17.833 --> 29:19.375
(growls)

29:26.875 --> 29:28.541
We're gonna need

29:26.875 --> 29:28.541
more firepower.

29:28.541 --> 29:30.208
Of course, it's on the

29:28.541 --> 29:30.208
other side of the room.

29:30.208 --> 29:31.416
I'll draw it away.

29:30.208 --> 29:31.416
Go. Go.

29:31.416 --> 29:32.708
Hey. Hey, hey!

29:34.625 --> 29:35.916
(growls)

29:43.166 --> 29:45.000
(phone ringing)

29:43.166 --> 29:45.000
Uh, Abbie?

29:45.000 --> 29:46.916
I need you to stop Nevins.

29:46.916 --> 29:47.958
He took Corbin's files.

29:51.875 --> 29:53.000
Crane, move!

29:53.000 --> 29:54.625
(gunshots)

29:54.625 --> 29:57.833
(gunshots)

29:54.625 --> 29:57.833
Abbie!

29:57.833 --> 29:59.833
You need to find Nevins;

29:57.833 --> 29:59.833
he'll be in the tunnels by now.

30:00.708 --> 30:02.750
(gunshots)

30:02.750 --> 30:04.916
(growls)

30:11.958 --> 30:13.125
I'm open to any ideas right now.

30:13.125 --> 30:15.041
(gunshot)

30:16.375 --> 30:17.208
The scarab.

30:18.750 --> 30:20.583
Target the scarab on his chest.

30:20.583 --> 30:22.708
It may be his

30:20.583 --> 30:22.708
proverbial Achilles heel.

30:23.458 --> 30:24.416
Go.

30:28.000 --> 30:30.208
Lieutenant!

30:37.541 --> 30:39.166
JENNY (in distance):

30:37.541 --> 30:39.166
He can't be far.

30:39.166 --> 30:40.375
He was playing us

30:39.166 --> 30:40.375
the whole time;

30:40.375 --> 30:41.583
I should've seen it.

30:41.583 --> 30:42.958
Later, okay?

30:42.958 --> 30:44.291
Hey, let's split up.

30:44.291 --> 30:46.291
We'll cover ground faster.

31:01.458 --> 31:03.458
(loud growl)

31:03.458 --> 31:05.875
Crane, I can't hit

31:03.458 --> 31:05.875
a target that small.

31:05.875 --> 31:08.041
Go. Go, go.

31:08.041 --> 31:09.916
Lieutenant! Lieutenant,

31:09.916 --> 31:11.166
you have this.

31:13.125 --> 31:14.458
(growls)

31:14.458 --> 31:15.291
(Crane grunts)

31:16.208 --> 31:17.041
Come on.

31:22.833 --> 31:23.833
Lieutenant!

31:25.708 --> 31:27.083
Come on, come on...

31:34.500 --> 31:36.375
Shoot it!

31:44.208 --> 31:46.625
(growls)

31:53.708 --> 31:55.750
Nice shooting, Mills.

31:55.750 --> 31:57.833
It's just about practice.

31:57.833 --> 31:59.791
(panting)

32:02.416 --> 32:03.750
Agent Foster.

32:03.750 --> 32:05.083
How's it going?

32:03.750 --> 32:05.083
All right.

32:05.083 --> 32:07.083
Can I ask you guys...

32:07.083 --> 32:09.166
are they all this ugly?

32:09.166 --> 32:11.083
Uh...

32:11.083 --> 32:12.416
actually, usually

32:11.083 --> 32:12.416
they're worse.

32:12.416 --> 32:14.833
This one's not too bad.

32:26.625 --> 32:28.583
Toss your weapon.

32:29.833 --> 32:31.083
This is your girl, here.

32:36.166 --> 32:38.041
You were family once.

32:38.041 --> 32:39.250
"Family."

32:39.250 --> 32:41.500
August Corbin hated me.

32:41.500 --> 32:44.416
He was just a holier-than-thou

32:41.500 --> 32:44.416
son of a bitch.

32:44.416 --> 32:45.750
He never gave in to temptation.

32:45.750 --> 32:47.750
He never took a bribe.

32:47.750 --> 32:50.916
You could literally choke

32:47.750 --> 32:50.916
on his saintliness.

32:50.916 --> 32:54.666
Don't you move.

32:59.041 --> 33:01.333
You know, I actually think my

32:59.041 --> 33:01.333
father meant a lot more to you

33:01.333 --> 33:03.750
than you're willing to admit.

33:03.750 --> 33:06.375
And I know how that is,

33:03.750 --> 33:06.375
believe me.

33:06.375 --> 33:08.166
I mean, I spent my whole life

33:08.166 --> 33:10.583
pretending like

33:08.166 --> 33:10.583
his opinion didn't matter to me.

33:10.583 --> 33:12.750
And I have just been trying

33:12.750 --> 33:16.625
for so long to understand him.

33:16.625 --> 33:20.375
And, you know what, man,

33:16.625 --> 33:20.375
I think I finally do.

33:20.375 --> 33:22.375
You loved him, Atticus.

33:22.375 --> 33:25.958
We both did.

33:25.958 --> 33:28.333
And you know damn well

33:25.958 --> 33:28.333
what he'd say to you right now.

33:31.750 --> 33:33.708
The hell with August Corbin.

33:37.333 --> 33:39.166
And the hell with you.

33:42.166 --> 33:44.166
(running footsteps departing)

33:57.833 --> 33:59.750
(sniffs)

33:59.750 --> 34:01.000
Hey.

34:01.000 --> 34:02.166
Hey.

34:04.750 --> 34:06.875
How are you?

34:06.875 --> 34:08.625
Well, I fought a ghoul

34:08.625 --> 34:10.625
so... horrible.

34:08.625 --> 34:10.625
(chuckles)

34:10.625 --> 34:11.541
(chuckles)

34:11.541 --> 34:13.708
Come here.

34:20.250 --> 34:22.250
(sighs)

34:22.250 --> 34:25.291
Nevins got away with the one

34:22.250 --> 34:25.291
document Corbin's been trying

34:25.291 --> 34:27.291
to keep from everyone

34:25.291 --> 34:27.291
for 20 years.

34:27.291 --> 34:30.291
Well, then we'll

34:27.291 --> 34:30.291
go get it back.

34:30.291 --> 34:33.291
You and I are getting pretty

34:30.291 --> 34:33.291
good at tracking stuff down.

34:33.291 --> 34:35.125
"Good"?

34:35.125 --> 34:37.125
We're the best.

34:37.125 --> 34:39.458
We're like Bonnie and Clyde.

34:39.458 --> 34:41.250
Minus the crime spree.

34:43.875 --> 34:46.041
You know how you said

34:43.875 --> 34:46.041
you would give anything

34:46.041 --> 34:49.041
for a few more minutes

34:46.041 --> 34:49.041
with your dad?

34:49.041 --> 34:52.791
You're not the only one

34:49.041 --> 34:52.791
who felt that way.

34:52.791 --> 34:55.833
But you made

34:52.791 --> 34:55.833
that happen for me.

34:58.083 --> 35:01.458
Nobody's ever done anything

34:58.083 --> 35:01.458
like that for me before.

35:01.458 --> 35:03.416
Well, you know,

35:03.416 --> 35:05.791
your dad took off on you

35:03.416 --> 35:05.791
when you were a kid.

35:05.791 --> 35:07.833
Mine was partners

35:05.791 --> 35:07.833
with a thief.

35:07.833 --> 35:10.916
So, uh, we got

35:07.833 --> 35:10.916
that in common.

35:10.916 --> 35:14.083
(chuckles)

35:14.083 --> 35:16.666
You know, I hated him

35:14.083 --> 35:16.666
for a long time.

35:16.666 --> 35:19.500
Thought he was...

35:16.666 --> 35:19.500
being more of a father

35:19.500 --> 35:22.583
to everyone else than

35:19.500 --> 35:22.583
he was to me, but...

35:22.583 --> 35:25.416
knowing the company

35:22.583 --> 35:25.416
he had to keep, the...

35:25.416 --> 35:28.666
the secrets that

35:25.416 --> 35:28.666
he had to protect...

35:30.333 --> 35:32.250
...I wish I could

35:30.333 --> 35:32.250
tell him just once

35:32.250 --> 35:34.666
that I think he was

35:32.250 --> 35:34.666
one hell of a guy.

35:35.875 --> 35:37.666
I envy that.

35:46.333 --> 35:50.083
♪ My sins from my youth ♪

35:50.083 --> 35:54.708
♪ Don't remember my sins... ♪

35:54.708 --> 35:56.416
I'd ask how you

35:54.708 --> 35:56.416
found me, but...

35:56.416 --> 35:58.750
you are a federal agent.

35:58.750 --> 36:00.625
I should have called.

36:00.625 --> 36:02.458
I'm just glad to see you.

36:02.458 --> 36:04.958
Yeah, Jenny wasn't gonna tell me

36:02.458 --> 36:04.958
that she'd seen you.

36:04.958 --> 36:06.875
But, you know, with her and I,

36:04.958 --> 36:06.875
it's hard to hide things

36:06.875 --> 36:08.416
for long, so...

36:09.375 --> 36:12.000
I came here

36:12.000 --> 36:17.583
because I need

36:12.000 --> 36:17.583
to ask you something about Mom.

36:17.583 --> 36:19.791
Right.

36:19.791 --> 36:21.875
When she began to unravel,

36:21.875 --> 36:23.166
what were

36:21.875 --> 36:23.166
the first signs?

36:23.166 --> 36:25.583
And how fast did it come on?

36:25.583 --> 36:28.208
Well, I-I don't remember

36:25.583 --> 36:28.208
how it started.

36:28.208 --> 36:30.291
It came in fits

36:28.208 --> 36:30.291
and starts.

36:30.291 --> 36:33.541
She'd be fine one minute

36:30.291 --> 36:33.541
and then having hallucinations

36:33.541 --> 36:35.583
the next. It was

36:33.541 --> 36:35.583
like she was living

36:35.583 --> 36:37.708
in two different realities.

36:37.708 --> 36:39.916
As it went along,

36:39.916 --> 36:41.375
she pushed me away,

36:39.916 --> 36:41.375
wouldn't let me in.

36:41.375 --> 36:43.250
And that's when you left us.

36:43.250 --> 36:46.250
Well, I started thinking maybe

36:43.250 --> 36:46.250
I was the problem, you know?

36:46.250 --> 36:48.916
Maybe if I wasn't around,

36:46.250 --> 36:48.916
things would get better.

36:48.916 --> 36:50.916
But, truthfully,

36:50.916 --> 36:52.375
I was just scared as hell.

36:52.375 --> 36:53.541
So was Mom.

36:53.541 --> 36:54.958
But she faced it

36:53.541 --> 36:54.958
all alone.

36:54.958 --> 36:56.875
She died alone.

36:56.875 --> 36:58.500
Hell, maybe that's

36:58.500 --> 37:00.083
in the cards

36:58.500 --> 37:00.083
for all of us.

37:00.083 --> 37:02.083
That's the way

37:00.083 --> 37:02.083
the Mills women kick off,

37:02.083 --> 37:03.750
crazy and alone.

37:03.750 --> 37:05.333
No. That's not gonna happen

37:03.750 --> 37:05.333
to you.

37:05.333 --> 37:06.333
You don't know that.

37:06.333 --> 37:08.625
You have no idea who I am.

37:08.625 --> 37:11.375
You don't know a lot

37:08.625 --> 37:11.375
about me either, Abbie.

37:11.375 --> 37:13.208
The one thing I know

37:11.375 --> 37:13.208
about our family,

37:13.208 --> 37:15.041
your mother's

37:13.208 --> 37:15.041
side and mine,

37:15.041 --> 37:16.958
is that we're strong people.

37:16.958 --> 37:18.583
Yeah, I've

37:16.958 --> 37:18.583
made mistakes.

37:18.583 --> 37:20.958
Had the hell

37:18.583 --> 37:20.958
knocked out of me.

37:20.958 --> 37:22.791
But I'm still standing.

37:22.791 --> 37:24.625
And so are you.

37:29.333 --> 37:31.791
You know what I remember?

37:33.291 --> 37:36.625
Um...

37:36.625 --> 37:39.625
your voice.

37:39.625 --> 37:41.625
Used to read stories to me,

37:41.625 --> 37:44.041
sing songs.

37:44.041 --> 37:46.791
I loved that voice.

37:49.000 --> 37:51.416
And I'm sorry

37:49.000 --> 37:51.416
you haven't heard it in a while.

37:51.416 --> 37:53.125
Me, too.

37:53.125 --> 37:54.875
But, Abbie,

37:54.875 --> 37:57.041
if you're going through

37:54.875 --> 37:57.041
something difficult right now,

37:57.041 --> 37:59.416
I want to help.

38:01.250 --> 38:04.000
Yeah, I have people

38:01.250 --> 38:04.000
for that now.

38:06.708 --> 38:09.500
Maybe one day.

38:14.708 --> 38:17.083
(phone rings)

38:19.958 --> 38:22.166
Are you avoiding my calls?

38:22.166 --> 38:25.333
Because it's been a few days

38:22.166 --> 38:25.333
since we last spoke.

38:25.333 --> 38:26.750
It's been a busy time.

38:26.750 --> 38:29.500
Any problems

38:26.750 --> 38:29.500
I should know about, Daniel?

38:29.500 --> 38:30.916
Such as?

38:30.916 --> 38:32.333
I've heard that Agent Mills

38:32.333 --> 38:34.958
is not as stable

38:32.333 --> 38:34.958
as she once was,

38:34.958 --> 38:36.958
that she's changed.

38:36.958 --> 38:38.875
Mills is a good agent.

38:38.875 --> 38:40.708
She'll find her feet again.

38:40.708 --> 38:43.666
Under your keen eye, Daniel,

38:40.708 --> 38:43.666
I have no doubt.

38:43.666 --> 38:45.916
Oh, one other thing:

38:43.666 --> 38:45.916
I want you to downgrade

38:45.916 --> 38:47.666
the search for Atticus Nevins.

38:47.666 --> 38:49.666
Minor resources only.

38:49.666 --> 38:51.750
Why the hell would I do that?

38:51.750 --> 38:54.750
Because I ordered you to.

38:56.750 --> 38:58.750
Satisfied?

39:00.958 --> 39:02.958
It's a start.

39:02.958 --> 39:04.375
The funds have already

39:02.958 --> 39:04.375
been transferred

39:04.375 --> 39:05.791
to your account in Geneva,

39:05.791 --> 39:07.500
and there is

39:05.791 --> 39:07.500
a plane standing by,

39:07.500 --> 39:09.458
waiting to take you

39:07.500 --> 39:09.458
wherever you choose.

39:09.458 --> 39:12.708
Oh, and I have a, uh,

39:09.458 --> 39:12.708
cash bonus for you.

39:15.791 --> 39:17.416
You have something for me.

39:19.333 --> 39:22.333
From the files

39:19.333 --> 39:22.333
of August Corbin.

39:22.333 --> 39:26.833
It's the exact coordinates

39:22.333 --> 39:26.833
of the nine sacred sites.

39:26.833 --> 39:29.125
Well, I can't tell you

39:26.833 --> 39:29.125
how much this means to us.

39:29.125 --> 39:31.083
Well, I don't really care.

39:31.083 --> 39:33.750
I just retired.

39:33.750 --> 39:36.125
Yes, Mr. Nevins...

39:36.125 --> 39:37.916
(gunshot)

39:37.916 --> 39:40.125
...you just did.

39:46.166 --> 39:48.250
Bologna on whole wheat?

39:48.250 --> 39:50.000
That is the Charlie Brown

39:48.250 --> 39:50.000
of sandwiches.

39:50.000 --> 39:53.000
The bald boy

39:50.000 --> 39:53.000
with awful luck?

39:53.000 --> 39:55.000
"Good grief."

39:53.000 --> 39:55.000
(chuckles)

39:55.000 --> 39:56.833
I take offense.

39:58.875 --> 40:00.875
I'll make us

39:58.875 --> 40:00.875
a real sandwich.

40:00.875 --> 40:02.583
And give me a hand.

40:07.791 --> 40:09.250
I see your wheels turning.

40:09.250 --> 40:10.666
Go on and ask.

40:10.666 --> 40:13.333
You saw your father.

40:13.333 --> 40:15.333
I did.

40:15.333 --> 40:17.291
I'm still processing it.

40:19.958 --> 40:23.375
By your tone, am I to assume

40:19.958 --> 40:23.375
this topic is to be shelved

40:23.375 --> 40:24.833
until later discussion?

40:24.833 --> 40:26.291
Nailed it.

40:26.291 --> 40:27.583
But I will talk about the fact

40:27.583 --> 40:29.083
that it has been hard lately,

40:29.083 --> 40:30.625
adjusting to being back,

40:30.625 --> 40:34.000
and I guess I want you to know

40:34.000 --> 40:35.541
that I am working on it.

40:37.541 --> 40:40.791
You have endured an ordeal

40:37.541 --> 40:40.791
few can even imagine.

40:40.791 --> 40:42.625
Except you.

40:42.625 --> 40:45.041
You know exactly what it's like

40:42.625 --> 40:45.041
to look around

40:45.041 --> 40:47.375
and everything

40:45.041 --> 40:47.375
is exactly the same

40:47.375 --> 40:50.666
but completely different.

40:55.708 --> 40:57.708
I'm trying really hard.

40:57.708 --> 40:59.500
And you will succeed.

41:01.791 --> 41:05.791
Just as you were by my side when

41:01.791 --> 41:05.791
I returned to Sleepy Hollow,

41:05.791 --> 41:07.791
so I shall be by yours.

41:07.791 --> 41:10.958
♪ ♪

41:10.958 --> 41:13.958
You know what

41:10.958 --> 41:13.958
I'm in the mood for?

41:13.958 --> 41:16.416
A beer.

41:13.958 --> 41:16.416
(sighs)

41:16.416 --> 41:19.416
A pint of ale to raise

41:16.416 --> 41:19.416
one's spirits aloft.

41:19.416 --> 41:22.291
And I believe Miss Jenny

41:19.416 --> 41:22.291
is tending bar

41:22.291 --> 41:23.666
at Mabie's Tavern this evening.

41:23.666 --> 41:25.291
Okay, you go, grab us a table.

41:25.291 --> 41:27.166
I need 20 minutes

41:25.291 --> 41:27.166
to finish some work.

41:27.166 --> 41:28.916
And then I'll pay

41:27.166 --> 41:28.916
for the next round.

41:28.916 --> 41:30.916
Very good.

41:32.083 --> 41:34.000
No, I want hot wings.

41:32.083 --> 41:34.000
Oh.

41:36.041 --> 41:39.458
No poultry is safe in

41:36.041 --> 41:39.458
Sleepy Hollow this dark night.

41:39.458 --> 41:40.625
(chuckles)

41:42.625 --> 41:44.458
(door opens, closes)

41:47.000 --> 41:49.000
♪ ♪

42:18.916 --> 42:20.916
♪ ♪

42:41.625 --> 42:44.500
You saved me.

42:44.500 --> 42:46.875
I'm yours.

